dc_title_s: Lidar-Derived 18-in Bare Earth DEM (ft) for La Crosse County, WI 2024
dc_description_s: This data represents a Lidar-derived 18-in Bare Earth Digital Elevation Model (DEM) for La Crosse County, Wisconsin in 2024.. This dataset has elevation values in feet and is in the WISCRS coordinate system for La Crosse County: EPSG 7615. A DEM represents the bare-Earth surface, removing all natural and built features.
uw_supplemental_s: Detailed metadata for the tiles used to create this countywide file:https://web.s3.wisc.edu/wsco-wisconsinview/lidar/La_Crosse/La_Crosse_2024_3DEP_Delivery/Metadata/Metadata.zip.
